Package com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.niox

Class Component

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.niox.Product
      • com.circa.mrv.grs_manager.niox.Component
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Consumable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Accessory
    public class Component
extends Product
implements Consumable
    The Component class extends the Product class and implements Consumable interface. It has a date the component was packaged, from which the expiration can be calculated. Component also has a serial number and product generation.
    Author:
    Arthur Vargas
